<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Set up admin – UPGS Panel</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/panel.css">
  <style>
    body { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 2rem 1rem; }
    .card { max-width: 420px; width: 100%; padding: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(45, 106, 79, 0.08); }
    .brand { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); letter-spacing: 0.02em; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .brand .ic { width: 28px; height: 28px; stroke: currentColor; fill: none; stroke-width: 2; stroke-linecap: round; stroke-linejoin: round; }
    .headline { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 0.35rem; }
    .tagline { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .notice { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-muted); background: #f0f7f1; }
    .setup-form label { display: block; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 0.35rem; }
    .setup-form input { width: 100%; padding: 0.6rem 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1rem; max-width: none; }
    .setup-form input:focus { box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(45, 106, 79, 0.15); }
    .setup-form input::placeholder { color: #95b5a8; }
    .setup-form button { width: 100%; padding: 0.65rem 1rem; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 0.25rem; }
    .setup-form button:hover { background: var(--color-primary-dark); }
    .setup-form button:focus { box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(45, 106, 79, 0.25); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1 class="brand">
      <svg class="ic" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
      UPGS Panel
    </h1>
    <p class="headline">First-time setup</p>
    <p class="tagline">Create the administrator account. You’ll use these credentials to log in.</p>
    <div class="notice" role="status">
      This panel runs with elevated privileges. Choose a strong password and keep it safe.
    </div>
    <form class="setup-form" method="post" action="/auth/setup">
      <label for="username">Username</label>
      <input type="text" id="username" name="username" value="admin" required autofocus placeholder="admin">
      <label for="password">Password</label>
      <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required placeholder="Choose a strong password">
      <button type="submit">Create admin account</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
